	<h1><span>The Cheesy, Sexed-Up &quot;8-Minute Abs&quot; Video Still Holds Up, 25 Years Later</span></h1>

			<h2><span>It made $20 million after its 1995 release for very good reason</span></h2>
	</div>
<!-- End Article Title -->

							<div class="article-grid grid-x grid-margin-x">
								<div class="main-content cell large-auto">
									<div class="grid-x grid-margin-x">
										<!-- Article Social -->
										<div class="cell large-shrink text-center sticky-parent">
											<div class="sticky-container">
